  <title>Scottish Fair Trade Forum : Scotland&#xE2;&#x20AC;&#x2122;s Fair Trade Nation</title>
  <description>This project will deliver Scotland&apos;s Fair Trade Nation Programme which will operate through a number of projects to increase the numbers of Fair Trade Towns, Fair Trade Zones and Fair Trade Higher Educational institutions throughout Scotland. These projects will be supported by media coverage and other campaigning to improve awareness and involvement through purchasing and volunteering within the Fair Trade supply chain. The programme also includes polling to assess progress. The objective is ensure longevity should Scottish Government funding come to an end.</description>
